snippet.textDisplay:
My boyfriend introduced this song to me in 2013. We were classmates then and just beginning to fall in love. I remember we used to discuss songs and movies. He used to keep the lyrics of this song as his WhatsApp status( ah! The nostagia of old whatsapp UI).  He told me this song talks about Shiv ji as Madaari. I instantly fell in love with the song.

Later we went on a trek to a shiv temple on a mountain , fell in love with each other under a waterfall lol, and that's when our love story started. It's been 12 years now that we are together and I honestly feel, Shivji blessed us and kept us together. We share the purest bond. Life is so strange when you look back in hindsight!
